high_descs: Turn around and find the square white table.
Pick up the green apple on the table.
Turn around and walk towards the sink.
Wash the apple in the sink and pick it back up.
Turn left and walk towards the small black table to your right.
Place the apple to the left of the grey cup on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed green apple on the black table.

high_descs: Turn around and head left to the white table.
Pick up the green apple on the table.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Wash the apple in the sink.
Walk left to the small black table.
Place the apple on the closest left corner of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed apple on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the small dining table on the left.
Pick up the apple from the table.
Turn around and walk forward to the sink.
Put the apple in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out of the sink.
Walk to the small end table to the left of the counter by the sink.
Put the apple on the table, to the left of the large black cup.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned apple on a small end table.
